Soni, Rishi (Cognizant) and Gangu, Gauthami (Cognizant): You can work on any of the below use cases 6 and 7.
Greenbank is an innovative, next-generation bank, powered by use cases from our Vibe Coding initiatives. We're dedicated to a sustainable future with Use cases like:
 
1.Conscious Commerce: We're introducing a new way to transact, where every purchase is evaluated by its positive or negative environmental impact.
 
2.Your Personal Carbon Dashboard: A cutting-edge feature that gives you a clear view of your carbon emissions, all tied to your spending habits.
 
3.Bringing Data to Life: See your environmental influence through engaging, intuitive visualizations that transform complex data into actionable insights.
 
4.Your Guide to Green: An intelligent AI chatbot is ready to answer questions and help you make eco-friendly choices.
 
5.Eco-Friendly Nudges: We provide personalized tips and recommendations to help you effortlessly become more environmentally conscious.
 
6.Green Investment Opportunities: Showcase eco-friendly investment options
 
7. Rewards System: Incentivize sustainable spending with better rates or rewards
 
